===Noun===
'''[[stop]] [[list]]'''
# {{computing}} A [[list]] of [[words]] or other data items which, for some special reason, should be ignored or bypassed by a particular data processing operation.
#: ''If you equip your search engine with a stop list containing a few common words such as "a", "the", and "and", you can decrease the full-text index size by about 20%.''
# (''media'') A list of people who subscribe to a publication (e.g., [[newspaper]]) and no longer wish to receive it.